  "admin_notices": [
    "D. Availability of Family-Sponsored and Employment-Based Visas: Immigrant visa issuance rates for aliens from certain countries have decreased due to various administration actions to protect national security. Dates for filing and final action dates have been advanced across various immigrant visa categories. Retrogression may be necessary later in FY2026.",
    "E. Extension of the Employment Fourth Religious Workers (SR) Category: H.R. 7148, signed February 3, 2026, extends the SR category until September 30, 2026.",
    "F. U.S. Government Employee Special Immigrant Visas (SIVs): The NDAA for FY2024 may affect current and former U.S. Government employees abroad applying for SIVs or adjustment of status."
